Project: The Wheel of Time — this Turn of the Wheel (muster roll)
Architect: David Lee Wise / ROOT0 / TriPod LLC
AI Collaborator: AVAN (Claude / Anthropic)
License: MIT

The current Turn of the Wheel sorted into specialty classes, channelers by Ajah
(canon colors). The One = Rand + Perrin + Mat, three ta'veren at a third each,
one total, set apart. Moiraine (Blue Ajah) leads the battalion. Classes: Blue/
Command, Yellow/Healing, Green/Battle, Brown/Knowledge, Red/Hunt, the Amyrlin,
the Forsaken (all+shadow), Warders, the Aiel, Undying Loyalty, and the One.
Characters by Robert Jordan & Brandon Sanderson, inspiration only.
